quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,37,"Dájúdájú ìrántí wà nínú ìyẹn fún ẹni tó ní ọkàn tàbí ẹni tó fi etí sílẹ̀, tó wà níbẹ̀ (pẹ̀lú ọkàn rẹ̀)."
  50,38,"Dájúdájú A ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀, ilẹ̀ àti n̄ǹkan tó wà láààrin àwọn méjèèjì fún ọjọ́ mẹ́fà. Kò sì rẹ̀ Wá rárá (áḿbọ̀sìbọ́sí pé A óò sinmi ní ọjọ́ keje)."
  50,39,"Nítorí náà, ṣe sùúrù lórí ohun tí wọ́n ń wí. Kí o sì ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ pẹ̀lú ẹyìn fún Olúwa Rẹ{1} ṣíwájú yíyọ òòrùn àti wíwọ̀ (rẹ̀)..",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ Allāhu kúrò níbi gbogbo àdínkù àti àbùkù, kí o sì yìn Ín lógo pé, O pé tán pátápátá.]
  51,31,"(Ànábì ’Ibrọ̄hīm) sọ pé: “Kí tún ni ọ̀rọ̀ tí ẹ bá wá, ẹ̀yin Òjíṣẹ́?”"
  51,32,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “Dájúdájú Wọ́n rán wa níṣẹ́ sí ìjọ ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ ni"
  51,33,"nítorí kí á lè fi òkúta amọ̀ (sísun) ránṣẹ́ sí wọn."
  52,22,"A máa fún wọn ní àlékún èso àti ẹran tí wọ́n nífẹ̀ẹ́ sí."
  52,23,"Wọn yó sì máa gba ife ọtí mu láààrin ara wọn nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra. Kò sí ọ̀rọ̀ ìsọkúsọ àti ìwà ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra."
  52,24,"Àwọn ọmọ-ọ̀dọ̀ wọn yó sì máa lọ bọ̀ láààrin wọn. (Wọ́n) dà bí àlúùúlù (òkúta olówó-iye-bíye) tí wọ́n fi pamọ́ sínú apó rẹ̀."
  53,16,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ohun tó bo igi Sidirah bò ó mọ́lẹ̀."
  53,17,"Ojú (Ànábì) kò yẹ̀, kò sì tayọ ẹnu-ààlà."
  53,18,"Dájúdájú ó rí nínú àwọn àmì Olúwa rẹ̀, tó tóbi."
  54,7,"Ojú wọn máa wálẹ̀ ní ti àbùkù. Wọn yó sì máa jáde láti inú sàréè bí ẹni pé eṣú tí wọ́n fọ́nká síta ni wọ́n."
  54,8,"Wọn yó sì máa yára lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ olùpèpè náà. Àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ yó sì wí pé: “Èyí ni ọjọ́ ìṣòro.”"
  54,9,"Ìjọ (Ànábì) Nūh pe òdodo ní irọ́ ṣíwájú wọn. Nígbà náà, wọ́n pe ẹrúsìn Wa ní òpùrọ́. Wọ́n sì wí pé: “Wèrè ni.” Wọ́n sì kọ̀ fún un pẹ̀lú ohùn líle.{1}.",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, wọ́n fi ohùn líle kọ òdodo sílẹ̀ fún Ànábì Nūh - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - ní kíkọ̀ àlésá-sẹ́yìn fún wọn nípasẹ̀ sísọ ọ̀rọ̀ burúkú sí i, híhalẹ̀ mọ̀ ọn, dídúnkokò mọ́ ọn nítorí kí ó lè máa wò wọ́n níran.]
  55,1,"Àjọkẹ́-ayé,"
  55,2,"Ó fi ìmọ̀ al-Ƙur’ān mọ (ẹni tí Ó fẹ́)."
  55,3,"Ó ṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn."